 Amanda Lukoff , from Arlington , Virginia , teamed up with her husband Danny Egan for their film The R-Word , which is in pre-production while they try to raise $ 200,000 for the documentary on the crowdsourcing website .
The director and producer was inspired to create the movie by her sister Gabrielle , has signed on cast members including Scrubs actor John C. McGinley and Lauren Potter , who has Down syndrome .